[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    325[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mPattern observation: the three HIGH architecture findings (conflict surfacing, retry fallback, idempotency) are the same shape.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m Each one names a required behavior in prose, builds part of the data structure for it, and then omits the implementation in the generation or orchestration step. The recipe's pattern of "name the failure mode, then walk past the fix" is worth flagging to the editor as a class of gap to watch for in later chapters.[K
